author: Danielle Berjikian
description:
According to Sleepy Joe, he can’t walk, but he can definitely beat “the hell out of” Jake Tapper for daring to question his mental competence, despite Tapper giving him a pass for over four years.

CNN cuts away as Joe Biden says he's *not* mentally unstable, suggests he would have won the election, and says he could "beat the hell" out of Jake Tapper.

Biden is out swinging today.

Biden was also seen getting up close and personal with a young reporter.

He also said that… pic.twitter.com/hcNKjmMttz
— Collin Rugg (@CollinRugg) May 30, 2025
title: Joe Biden returns, where he threatens to beat up Jake Tapper and admits he's NOT mentally stable
